pull_commit_message: Complete rewrite for version 1.0

pullsbody:
Improvement of Nmap plugin with new features, with complete parsing of XML output. New main feats are:
- each issue is associated to an IP (allowing precise identification in case of CIDR target)
- severity of issue for open port is configurable
- a baseline can be configured to allow open ports on specific IP
- service leaking specific version will raise an issue with white-list

I know this is a lot to process but I am willing to explain our modifications and open to suggestions.

Best regards
